title: Capturing A Military Base In Rocks [Action, Eng, 2018]
description:
On one of the islands hidden in the ocean, a base for training terrorists was found among the rocks.
Your task is to destroy the base with a group of elite soldiers. Do not forget to destroy the helicopter, otherwise the leaders will be able to get away.
This task is not as simple as it seemed at first glance. Soldiers of the enemy have received excellent training and even superior armament.
After landing, look for a hut with weapons and ammunition. Collect weapons and destroy terrorists.
